  "1806330": {
    "name": "Lavender Quartz 边界震荡",
    "steam_appid": 1806330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一部无分支结局的视觉小说。 两道命运线追寻着希望而来，在原点交错，走向一个终局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/908afb87a73fcf14ef313bd79ca0960d.avif?t=1755756768\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras_big/908afb87a73fcf14ef313bd79ca0960d.avif?t=1755756768 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>        </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>         那之后我一直被某种思绪所苦。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>                      我一直觉得自己逃避了什么。虽然没有任何人这样对我说过。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>                                        但我一直听得到一个声音说我在逃避。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战争开始至今已过去四年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在依柯努的故里被占领后，她逃到了州府米拉纳尔克避难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一天晚上，她目睹了到一颗卫星坠入荒野。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >国家亲卫队在该坠落地区试图搜寻着什么东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但那个东西已被一个神秘的少年捡走了，除了依柯努，其他人都看不见这位少年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在好奇心的驱使下，依柯努跟着少年来到了一个古老的设施。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在那里，他遇到了自称是政府特工的女子 奇尔希姆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当依柯努问她卫星里封藏的是什么时，女子说道：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那是一种超自然的物质，一种 “原石”，有能力推翻失控的战争局势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >依柯努问。    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　　<strong>「如果帮你找回原石，我能改变些什么吗？我能回到我的故乡去吗？」<i> </i></strong>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇尔希姆回答。    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>　　　「 ……嗯，应该能。如果政府拿到了原石，那苛责你的声音，应该也不会再出现了。”」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Lavender Quartz  边界震荡》是视觉小说，讲述了在某个战时城市中发生的一系列事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/d4ce562bf370919ee4b8849d073eea0b.avif?t=1755756768\" width=616 height=325 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公 依柯努 开始追踪一个神秘少年，他从坠落的卫星里拿走了一些东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/80ab55157b29aac2a3ff39951c85a698.avif?t=1755756768\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras_big/80ab55157b29aac2a3ff39951c85a698.avif?t=1755756768 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >依柯努 遇到了情报员 奇尔希姆，后者在城市里四处搜集有关少年和超自然物质 “原石 ”的线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/bf753e753e630b46c80a7cfd281ebcd1.poster.avif?t=1755756768\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/bf753e753e630b46c80a7cfd281ebcd1.webm?t=1755756768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/bf753e753e630b46c80a7cfd281ebcd1.mp4?t=1755756768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事情很快急转直下，依柯努被迫面对残酷的事实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/e7e822c8f5f9b2f28843f1c121225df7.avif?t=1755756768\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras_big/e7e822c8f5f9b2f28843f1c121225df7.avif?t=1755756768 width=800 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>依柯努</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名住在州府米拉纳尔克的大学生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战争爆发前他逃离故乡以来，她一直试图通过收集和分析互联网上的公开信息，来从平民的角度改变战争局势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她对家乡有着超乎寻常的好奇心和痴迷，因此做出了有时看似鲁莽的冲动行为。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她在 “原石 ”中找到了回家的希望，并决定与 奇尔希姆 合作，即便他深知其中的风险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/a7f56ef36b884d632cbb834bbbd28ea5.avif?t=1755756768\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras_big/a7f56ef36b884d632cbb834bbbd28ea5.avif?t=1755756768 width=800 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奇尔希姆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隶属于情报机构的神秘女子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她来到州府米拉纳尔克，想从坠落的卫星上取回原石，却发现一个男孩抢先了她一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她与同样在寻找原石的国家亲卫队不和，为了比亲卫队抢占先机，她让 依柯努 参与了进来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras/698f26d21950dbc14527ba4894f30b5e.avif?t=1755756768\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806330/extras_big/698f26d21950dbc14527ba4894f30b5e.avif?t=1755756768 width=800 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>少年</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出现在卫星坠落现场的一个神秘少年，他带走了原石。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少年有一种特殊能力，可以隐身，并让任何人都无法记住他。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他还袭击了 奇尔希姆，但原因不明。</p>",
